Position
The focus of this JR DevOps Engineer will be on Operations development. This group is looking to build the best-in-class automated reports, build out change management templates, work on custom built .NET application, and use SQL/PowerBI for metrics.

Job Description
• Responsible for first class JIRA administration.
• Assist teams in buildings custom integrations between tools.
• Assist in building centralized data reporting from multiple sources.
• Responsible for facilitating collaboration in a fast paced, DevOps oriented environment while working independently with a high level of self-motivation.
